experiment

Each experiment XML configuration file must have one EXPERIMENT element of which only one is permitted and it must contain all other elements of the configuration file.

<experimentappNameDisplay="String"
appNameInternal="String Lowercase"
backgroundColour="RGB Hex Value"
complementColour0="RGB Hex Value"
complementColour1="RGB Hex Value"
complementColour2="RGB Hex Value"
complementColour3="RGB Hex Value"
complementColour4="RGB Hex Value"
primaryColour0="RGB Hex Value"
primaryColour1="RGB Hex Value"
primaryColour2="RGB Hex Value"
primaryColour3="RGB Hex Value"
primaryColour4="RGB Hex Value"
isScalable="Boolean"
preserveLastState="Boolean"
userIdGetParam="String (optional)"
rotatable="Boolean"
showMenuBar="Boolean"
defaultScale="Decimal Number"
textFontSize="Integral Number"
>
<preventWindowClosefeatureText="String"
>
<administration>
<scss>
<metadata>
<presenterself="String"
title="String (optional)"
menuLabel="String (optional)"
back="String (optional)"
next="String (optional)"
type="Option List [transmission, metadata, preload, stimulus, colourPicker, colourReport, kindiagram, menu, debug, text, timeline]"
>
<stimuli>
</experiment>

preventWindowClose

When true the a popup will warn before closing the browser window by showing the message in 'featureText'. Not all browsers will respect this in the same way, so test this on the intended platforms.

<preventWindowClosefeatureText="String"
/>

administration

Administration

<administration>
<dataChannellabel="String"
logToSdCard="Boolean"
channel="Integral Number"
>
</administration>

<dataChannellabel="String"

/>

scss



<scss>

</scss>

metadata

The fields of data to be collected for each participant and for use as storage data that will be reported in the admin tables.

<metadata>
<fieldcontrolledMessage="String"
controlledRegex="String"
postName="String"
registrationField="String"
duplicatesControlledMessage="String (optional)"
preventServerDuplicates="Boolean (optional)"
>
</metadata>

field



<fieldcontrolledMessage="String"
controlledRegex="String"
postName="String"
registrationField="String"
duplicatesControlledMessage="String (optional)"
preventServerDuplicates="Boolean (optional)"
/>

stimuli

All stimulus elements must be contained in the stimuli element.

<stimuli>
<stimulusidentifier="String"
videoPath="String (optional)"
imagePath="String (optional)"
code="String (optional)"
audioPath="String (optional)"
label="String (optional)"
correctResponses="String (optional)"
ratingLabels="String (optional)"
tags="String (optional)"
pauseMs="Integral Number (optional)"
>
</stimuli>

stimulus

Each individual stimulus can be described in the form of label, audio, video

<stimulusidentifier="String"
videoPath="String (optional)"
imagePath="String (optional)"
code="String (optional)"
audioPath="String (optional)"
label="String (optional)"
correctResponses="String (optional)"
ratingLabels="String (optional)"
tags="String (optional)"
pauseMs="Integral Number (optional)"
/>
